ğŸ’ Premium Auto-Login (Refined)
ProtocolLib Removed: The plugin no longer requires ProtocolLib to function. It now uses a stable IP-Trust System.
Logic Change:
Players use /premium to verify their account with Mojang API.
The plugin saves their current IP address.
Auto-Login only occurs if the player joins from that exact trusted IP.
If the IP changes, the plugin falls back to requesting a password for security.
